remarks.format: ## Remarks 序列点用于在源文件位置和 IL 偏移量之间进行映射。Sequence points are used to map between source file locations and IL offsets. 每个序列点都由与对象相关的起始和结束行/列号指定的 IL 偏移量和源文件区域组成 。Each sequence point consists of an IL offset and source file region, specified by start and end line/column numbers relative to an object. 每个数组的特定索引处的每个元素都对应于一个特定的序列点。Each element at a specific index of every array corresponds to a specific sequence point. 每行和每列都定义方法中语句的开头。Each line and each column defines the start of a statement within a method. 应按偏移量的递增顺序对数组进行排序。The arrays should be sorted in the increasing order of offsets. 偏移量始终是从方法开始处的偏移量（以字节为单位）。The offset is always the offset from the start of the method, in bytes.
